        <section purpose="didigetthis">
            <title>Did I Get This?</title>
            <body>
                <p>A flight has been overbooked; however, there are
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101644-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101642-0500" content="two"?>
                    seats
                    available<?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101714-0500" content=" - "?><?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101717-0500"?>&#8212;<?oxy_insert_end?>one
                    in business class and one in first class. The ground crew decides to upgrade
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T102332-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T102331-0500" content="two"?>
                    of the coach (regular class) passengers so that
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101732-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101731-0500" content="two"?>
                    more passengers will be able to get on the flight. The crew has identified
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101755-0500"?>4<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101754-0500" content="four"?>
                    passengers,
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T102345-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T102343-0500" content="two"?>
                    males and
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T102347-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T102347-0500" content="two"?>
                    females, who are traveling by themselves and who have been loyal frequent fliers
                    o<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101832-0500"?>n<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101832-0500" content="f"?>
                    the airline. They decide to choose
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101841-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101839-0500" content="two"?>
                    of
                    th<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101844-0500"?>ose<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101843-0500" content="e"?>
                    passengers at random for the upgrade. The first chosen will be upgraded to first
                    class, and the second chosen will be upgraded to business class. We'll denote
                    the
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101904-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101902-0500" content="two"?>
                    males and
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101907-0500"?>2<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101906-0500" content="two"?>
                    females (as before)
                    <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101913-0500"?>with<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101912-0500" content="by"?>
                    M1<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101916-0500"?>,<?oxy_insert_end?>
                    M2<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101917-0500"?>,<?oxy_insert_end?>
                    F1<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T101920-0500"?>
                    and<?oxy_insert_end?> F2.</p>
                <wb:inline idref="u3_m1_outcomes2_tutor2" purpose="didigetthis"/>
